[size=4][b]Heads-up[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you turn the [b]plant in any season[/b] toggle [i]off[/i] mid-save, any out-of-season crops already in the ground will die immediately on the next day-roll. Harvest them first if you want to keep them. Turning the toggle [i]on[/i] is always safe.[/size]

[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Plant any seed in any season on any farm type, buy out-of-season seeds, and make every crop regrowable. Each option toggles independently.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Plant in any season[/b] — strawberries in winter, pumpkins in spring; the season check is bypassed.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Plant on any farm[/b] — your farm type (Land, Sea, Sky) no longer restricts which crops you can plant where.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Buy out-of-season seeds[/b] — the farming shop's stock isn't gated by current season; everything's always available.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Regrowable crops[/b] — every crop becomes regrowable instead of one-and-done. The exact regrow timing follows the vanilla rules for crops that already regrow.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Independent toggles[/b] — every option above is its own switch; pick what you want and leave the rest off.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/207]Museum Sell Price Redux[/url] — once you're farming year-round, museum items become a real income stream.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — broader QoL grab-bag; quick-save and auto-load are handy when experimenting with crop layouts.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/8]Cheat Enabler[/url] — [font=Courier New]/finditemid[/font] makes hunting down obscure seeds for testing a lot quicker.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...\steamapps\common\Sun Haven\BepInEx\plugins[/code][/size]

